# Inbox folder for qc-site-map

Skill `qc-dashboard-sync` writes `dashboard-orphans.md` into this folder when
bottom-up adds a UC row that is not present in the current site-map handoff.

Skill `qc-site-map` Mode 3 consumes (and deletes) that file when it reconciles
each orphan UC against the existing site-map.

This `.gitkeep` is the only file committed; the inbox is otherwise transient.
